devdoc.details: The Election Administrator Contract contains the information of all election administrators. Due to the nature of the elections,  the election administrators' addresses will change over time. Therefore a seperate logical contract is a good idea to keep track of such changes.  The majority of an administration's functions will be on the election contracts.
